└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Integration Hooks

### Pre-Session Validation
- Verify tool availability and configuration
- Check TDD Guard status and project setup
- Validate SDD project initialization if applicable
- Confirm required environment variables and access

### Mid-Session Checkpoints
- Validate progress against stated goals every 5 actions
- Check context window usage and plan compression if needed
- Confirm tool performance and switch if suboptimal
- Update session logs with current progress

### Post-Session Cleanup
- Archive conversation state for future reference
- Update project-level tracking files if they exist
- Clean up temporary files and test artifacts
- Generate session summary for handoff documentation

## Artifact Management

### File State Tracking
Always maintain awareness of:
- Files read during session (with timestamps)
- Files modified during session (with change summaries)
- Files created during session (with purposes)
- Dependencies between files (impact analysis)

### Session Continuity
- Preserve context for follow-up sessions
- Document incomplete work with next steps
- Track cumulative progress across multiple sessions
- Maintain tool selection reasoning for consistency

